sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as Coordinator
    participant RA as Worker-A
    participant RB as Worker-B
    participant RC as Worker-C
    participant WI as Impl-Worker
    participant WV as Verify-Worker

    U->>C: Add OAuth to login
    par Research
        C->>RA: Research login code
        C->>RB: Research OAuth practices
        C->>RC: Research test coverage
    end

    RA-->>C: task-notification
    RB-->>C: task-notification
    RC-->>C: task-notification
    Note over C: Synthesize into self-contained spec

    C->>WI: Implementation spec
    Note over WI: One at a time per file set
    WI-->>C: task-notification

    C->>WV: Verification task
    Note over WV: Independent adversarial verify
    WV-->>C: VERDICT PASS or FAIL

    C->>U: Synthesized report
